comments:
If a project contains a file META-INF/MANIFEST.MF that does not have a line

Bundle-SymbolicName: ...

The the JET builder will fail. Other JET components may also fail, and in some cases, the JET plug-in will fail to load.

Log contain may messages such as:

Skipping builder org.eclipse.jet.builder for project WIDSetupPattern. Either the builder is missing from the install, or it belongs to a project nature that is missing or disabled.

Or

Error
Fri Nov 10 13:54:07 EST 2006
An error occurred while automatically activating bundle org.eclipse.jet (92).

org.osgi.framework.BundleException: Exception in org.eclipse.jet.internal.InternalJET2Platform.start() of bundle org.eclipse.jet.
...


OR

!ENTRY org.eclipse.core.resources 4 2 2006-11-09 21:57:08.687
!MESSAGE Problems occurred when invoking code from plug-in: "org.eclipse.core.resources".
!STACK 0
java.lang.NullPointerException
	at org.eclipse.jet.internal.runtime.BundleManifest.getSymbolicName(Unknown Source)
...
